spec_data.Name: ampache_browser
spec_data.Description:
Ampache Browser is a library that implements desktop client access to
the Ampache service (http://ampache.org). It provides end-user Qt UI and
has a simple C++ interface that allows easy integration into client
applications.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 17 Sep 2017 05:02:26 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: C++ and Qt based client library for Ampache access
